Copyright (C) 2013 Phong V. Cao <phongvcao@phongvcao.com>


==================
Basic Installation
==================
-------------------------------------------------
1. First learn how to deploy Django on HostGator:
-------------------------------------------------
   
   * http://roshanbook.wordpress.com/2011/11/08/getting-django-up-and-running-on-hostgator/
    
   (If the above link no longer works then please extract the file deploy_django_hostgator.tar.gz)


------------------------
2. Install static files:
------------------------

   * dingoprojectorg/static/ should be installed in public_html/ folder


------------------------------
3. Deploy configuration files:
------------------------------

   * files in public_html/ should be installed in public_html/ folder

